  <title>Login: Peek Into Campfire</title>
  <link href="http://www.karthikc.campfirenow.com/stylesheets/screen.css?1210305079" media="all" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
  <link href="http://www.karthikc.campfirenow.com/stylesheets/backpack-styles-for-login.css?1210305079" 
    media="all" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
  <%=stylesheet_link_tag 'login' %>
  <script src="/javascripts/prototype.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <script src="/javascripts/effects.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
</head>

<body class="modal login ">
  <div id="Container">
    <div id="Modal">
      <p id="peekinto_warning">
        Note: This is <span class="emphasize">not</span> the <a href="http://www.campfirenow.com/">real campfire</a> login page. 
      </p>
      <% if flash[:error] %>
        <div id="errorMessage" class="flash alert"><%= flash[:error] %></div>
      <% end %>
      <div class="inner">
        <div id="peekinto">Peek Into <br/> Campfire</div>
        <form action="/authenticate" id="loginForm" method="post">
          <dl>
            <dt>Account:</dt>
            <dd><input id="sub_domain" name="sub_domain" value="<%=params[:sub_domain]%>" type="text" />.campfirenow.com</dd>
            <dt>Email:</dt>
            <dd><input id="email_address" name="email_address" value="<%=params[:email_address]%>" type="text" /></dd>
            <dt>Password:</dt>
            <dd><input id="password" name="password" value="<%=params[:password]%>" type="password" /></dd>
            <dd><input alt="Login" type="submit" value ="Login"/></dd>
          </dl>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div id="peekinto_info">
      <div id="peekinto_info_title">What is Peek Into Campfire ?</div>
      <div id="peekinto_info_message">
        Peek Into Campfire is a new way to view your <a href="http://www.campfirenow.com/">Campfire</a> transcripts. It collects the most recent messages from all your rooms, into a single page. The messages are grouped by room and are rearranged to show the recently updated rooms at the top. It also reduces clutter by removing messages that indicate people entering or leaving a room.
        <br/><br/>
        Peek Into Campfire does not store or use your Campfire password for any other purpose. It is an open source application hosted on <a href="http://github.com/karthikc/peek/tree/master">github</a>. Please send in your comments, suggestions or feedback to me <a href="mailto:karthik.cs@gmail.com">via email</a>.
        </div>
    </div>
    
  </div>
  
  <div id="peekinto_footer">
    <a href="http://www.campfirenow.com/">Campfire</a> is a product of 
    <a href="http://www.37signals.com/">37signals</a>, LLC and a reserved trademark.
  </div>
